channel.title: Preview of my Client and New Server-Project 69
channel.description: Hey guys,This is a preview of my client-Comes with skillcapes/hood,black phat,and bandos godsword. I coded them in all the right places.This is also a preview of Project 69. I've added Woodcutting/Smelting/smithing/Fishing into my server.I've been working on it for about 1-2 days now.I made the client a while ago(It was made for Penguinscape v.2) Anyways here are some pics. Give me some feedback [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img266.imageshack.us/img266/7179/woodcuttingmy2.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img91.imageshack.us/img91/3752/skillcapeshopan3.png[/img][/URL] You need the client to play on the server. That's All I'm releasing for now. I need more ideas also Post suggestions-I'm open to them :P Also a Kdbcave and other fun things to do on the server
